Century College Clothing Closet: Clothes Pins
West Campus Room - W1010

Students can come to the Clothes Pins to shop for gently used clothing for themselves and children for free. All they need is either a student ID card or student ID number. All current students are eligible to use Clothes Pins.

Hours:
Monday and Wednesday - 12 pm - 4 pm
Tuesday - 1 - 3 pm
Thursday - 9 am - 3 pm
Friday - 10 am - 4 pm
Also available by appointment - phone number to W1010 is 651-779-5765.

You can also stop by the Resource and Support Center during Mondays - Thursdays at 9 AM - 4 PM or Fridays at 9 AM - 2:00 PM and we can help you to access Clothes Pins. View flier at: Clothes Pins Flier.

Contact: 651-779-3221 - Michele Jersak, Counselor
